{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_013KgSyrMqrtAmwXBPuCP9Lp","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to generate 10 realistic fake OCR recipe text files with specific patterns. Let me break down the requirements:\n\n1. Save to: tools/title-loop/input/{RECIPE_TITLE}.generated.22.txt\n2. Filenames: Use SPACES, preserve Polish diacritics\n3. Recipes: ~60% English, ~40% Polish. Mix of categories and title lengths\n4. Avoid existing recipes listed\n5. Pattern requirements:\n   - 5 files with SPILLOVER: 40-60 lines, corrupted text from previous recipe before real title\n   - 3 files with OCR_CORRUPTION: Character corruption throughout (digit for letter, dotless i, hyphenation artifacts, garbage)\n   - 2 files with SIMPLE: Basic OCR noise, 15-60 lines\n\nLet me create 10 unique recipes:\n\nENGLISH (6):\n1. Roasted Garlic Broccoli - SPILLOVER\n2. Lemon Herb Grilled Chicken - OCR_CORRUPTION\n3. Beet and Goat Cheese Salad - SPILLOVER\n4. Chocolate Chip Cookies - SIMPLE\n5. Tomato Basil Pasta - OCR_CORRUPTION\n6. Berry Tart - SPILLOVER\n\nPOLISH (4):\n7. Żurek - OCR_CORRUPTION\n8. Obwarzanek Warszawski - SPILLOVER\n9. Kielbasa z Cebulą - SIMPLE\n10. Placki Ziemniaczane - OCR_CORRUPTION\n\nLet me create each one with the proper patterns:\n\n1. Roasted Garlic Broccoli (SPILLOVER - 45 lines)\n2. Lemon Herb Grilled Chicken (OCR_CORRUPTION)\n3. Beet and Goat Cheese Salad (SPILLOVER - 50 lines)\n\n\n4. Chocolate Chip Cookies (SIMPLE - 25 lines)\n5. Tomato Basil Pasta (OCR_CORRUPTION)\n6. Berry Tart (SPILLOVER - 55 lines)\n7. Żurek (OCR_CORRUPTION)\n8. Obwarzanek Warszawski (SPILLOVER - 48 lines)\n9. Kielbasa z Cebulą (SIMPLE - 20 lines)\n10. Placki Ziemniaczane (OCR_CORRUPTION)\n\nNow I'll generate each file with appropriate corruption patterns and line counts, ensuring filenames use spaces and preserve diacritics correctly.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":94776,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":94776},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2ce049df-e6ec-43f0-8acf-b8060ae53121","uuid":"b5f3a4f0-f4f9-46d6-afe9-b3983b171a41"}
